{
  "video_id": "Fcm-mAwPkxg",
  "title": "Say your truths and seek them in others | Elizabeth Lesser",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13840.0,
      "end_time": 14794.0,
      "text": "Like many of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14818.0,
      "end_time": 17189.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had several careers in my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17214.0,
      "end_time": 19365.0,
      "text": "and although they&#39;ve been varied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19389.0,
      "end_time": 23276.0,
      "text": "my first job set the foundation for all of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23300.0,
      "end_time": 27313.0,
      "text": "I was a home-birth midwife throughout my 20s."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27623.0,
      "end_time": 32747.0,
      "text": "Delivering babies taught me valuable and sometimes surprising things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32771.0,
      "end_time": 35541.0,
      "text": "like how to start a car at 2am."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35565.0,
      "end_time": 37363.0,
      "text": "when it&#39;s 10 degrees below zero."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37387.0,
      "end_time": 38388.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38412.0,
      "end_time": 42747.0,
      "text": "Or how to revive a father who&#39;s fainted at the sight of blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42771.0,
      "end_time": 43822.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43846.0,
      "end_time": 46291.0,
      "text": "Or how to cut the umbilical cord just so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46316.0,
      "end_time": 48537.0,
      "text": "to make a beautiful belly button."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48561.0,
      "end_time": 52346.0,
      "text": "But those aren&#39;t the things that stuck with me or guided me"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52370.0,
      "end_time": 56354.0,
      "text": "when I stopped being a midwife and started other jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56378.0,
      "end_time": 60471.0,
      "text": "What stuck with me was this bedrock belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60495.0,
      "end_time": 65506.0,
      "text": "that each one of us comes into this world with a unique worth."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66282.0,
      "end_time": 69652.0,
      "text": "When I looked into the face of a newborn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70192.0,
      "end_time": 73884.0,
      "text": "I caught a glimpse of that worthiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73909.0,
      "end_time": 76751.0,
      "text": "that sense of unapologetic selfhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76775.0,
      "end_time": 78951.0,
      "text": "that unique spark."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80586.0,
      "end_time": 84343.0,
      "text": "I use the word \"soul\" to describe that spark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84367.0,
      "end_time": 89600.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s the only word in English that comes close to naming"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89300.0,
      "end_time": 91742.0,
      "text": "what each baby brought into the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92623.0,
      "end_time": 97291.0,
      "text": "Every newborn was as singular as a snowflake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 97315.0,
      "end_time": 100686.0,
      "text": "a matchless mash-up of biology"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100710.0,
      "end_time": 103374.0,
      "text": "and ancestry and mystery."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103914.0,
      "end_time": 106310.0,
      "text": "And then that baby grows up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106550.0,
      "end_time": 108170.0,
      "text": "and in order to fit into the family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108194.0,
      "end_time": 110235.0,
      "text": "to conform to the culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 110259.0,
      "end_time": 112529.0,
      "text": "to the community, to the gender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113174.0,
      "end_time": 116116.0,
      "text": "that little one begins to cover its soul,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 116140.0,
      "end_time": 117654.0,
      "text": "layer by layer."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118197.0,
      "end_time": 119911.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re born this way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120405.0,
      "end_time": 121563.0,
      "text": "but --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121587.0,
      "end_time": 123179.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123203.0,
      "end_time": 126192.0,
      "text": "But as we grow, a lot of things happen to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 126640.0,
      "end_time": 128500.0,
      "text": "that make us ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 129815.0,
      "end_time": 134959.0,
      "text": "want to hide our soulful eccentricities and authenticity."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134983.0,
      "end_time": 136350.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve all done this."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 136374.0,
      "end_time": 139213.0,
      "text": "Everyone in this room is a former baby --"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139237.0,
      "end_time": 140259.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140283.0,
      "end_time": 142768.0,
      "text": "with a distinctive birthright."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 143560.0,
      "end_time": 148776.0,
      "text": "But as adults, we spend so much of our time uncomfortable in our own skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148800.0,
      "end_time": 152778.0,
      "text": "like we have ADD: authenticity deficit disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153449.0,
      "end_time": 155570.0,
      "text": "But not those babies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155810.0,
      "end_time": 156322.0,
      "text": "not yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156347.0,
      "end_time": 158125.0,
      "text": "Their message to me was:"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158453.0,
      "end_time": 160704.0,
      "text": "uncover your soul"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160728.0,
      "end_time": 163921.0,
      "text": "and look for that soul-spark"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163945.0,
      "end_time": 165155.0,
      "text": "in everyone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 165179.0,
      "end_time": 166402.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s still there."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167172.0,
      "end_time": 169934.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s what I learned from laboring women."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 170414.0,
      "end_time": 173414.0,
      "text": "Their message was about staying open,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 173438.0,
      "end_time": 175665.0,
      "text": "even when things are painful."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 176584.0,
      "end_time": 179120.0,
      "text": "A woman&#39;s cervix normally looks like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179360.0,
      "end_time": 181186.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a tight little muscle"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 181210.0,
      "end_time": 182837.0,
      "text": "at the base of the uterus."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 183243.0,
      "end_time": 186628.0,
      "text": "And during labor, it has to stretch from this"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 187576.0,
      "end_time": 188958.0,
      "text": "to this."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 188982.0,
      "end_time": 190245.0,
      "text": "Ouch!"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 190269.0,
      "end_time": 192875.0,
      "text": "If you fight against that pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193343.0,
      "end_time": 195270.0,
      "text": "you just create more pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 195510.0,
      "end_time": 197807.0,
      "text": "and you block what wants to be born."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 198482.0,
      "end_time": 202320.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll never forget the magic that would happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 202344.0,
      "end_time": 204987.0,
      "text": "when a woman stopped resisting the pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 206185.0,
      "end_time": 207472.0,
      "text": "and opened."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 207496.0,
      "end_time": 210663.0,
      "text": "It was as if the forces of the universe took notice"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 211211.0,
      "end_time": 213306.0,
      "text": "and sent in a wave of help."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213973.0,
      "end_time": 215895.0,
      "text": "I never forgot that message,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 215919.0,
      "end_time": 219939.0,
      "text": "and now, when difficult or painful things happen to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219963.0,
      "end_time": 221501.0,
      "text": "in my life or my work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 221909.0,
      "end_time": 224536.0,
      "text": "of course at first I resist them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 224561.0,
      "end_time": 227785.0,
      "text": "but then I remember what I learned from the mothers:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 227809.0,
      "end_time": 229142.0,
      "text": "stay open."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 229508.0,
      "end_time": 230937.0,
      "text": "Stay curious."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 230961.0,
      "end_time": 233666.0,
      "text": "Ask the pain what it&#39;s come to deliver."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 234170.0,
      "end_time": 236475.0,
      "text": "Something new wants to be born."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 237311.0,
      "end_time": 239609.0,
      "text": "And there was one more big soulful lesson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 239633.0,
      "end_time": 242427.0,
      "text": "and that one I learned from Albert Einstein."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 242769.0,
      "end_time": 244725.0,
      "text": "He wasn&#39;t at any of the births, but --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 244749.0,
      "end_time": 245781.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 245805.0,
      "end_time": 248447.0,
      "text": "It was a lesson about time."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 249732.0,
      "end_time": 253885.0,
      "text": "At the end of his life, Albert Einstein concluded"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 253909.0,
      "end_time": 258580.0,
      "text": "that our normal, hamster-wheel experience of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 258829.99999999997,
      "end_time": 259429.99999999997,
      "text": "is an illusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 259843.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262236.0,
      "text": "We run round and round, faster and faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 263883.0,
      "text": "trying to get somewhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 264455.0,
      "end_time": 266438.0,
      "text": "And all the while,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 267218.0,
      "end_time": 270647.0,
      "text": "underneath surface time is this whole other dimension"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 271288.0,
      "end_time": 275987.0,
      "text": "where the past and the present and the future merge"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 276367.0,
      "end_time": 278940.0,
      "text": "and become deep time."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 279414.0,
      "end_time": 282109.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s nowhere to get to."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 282716.0,
      "end_time": 287650.0,
      "text": "Albert Einstein called this state, this dimension,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 287890.0,
      "end_time": 288750.0,
      "text": "\"only being.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 288774.0,
      "end_time": 290730.0,
      "text": "And he said when he experienced it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 290754.0,
      "end_time": 293610.0,
      "text": "he knew sacred awe."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 293818.0,
      "end_time": 295467.0,
      "text": "When I was delivering babies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 295491.0,
      "end_time": 297385.0,
      "text": "I was forced off the hamster wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 297410.0,
      "end_time": 301189.0,
      "text": "Sometimes I had to sit for days, hours and hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 301213.0,
      "end_time": 303799.0,
      "text": "just breathing with the parents;"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 303823.0,
      "end_time": 305159.0,
      "text": "just being."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 305659.0,
      "end_time": 308615.0,
      "text": "And I got a big dose of sacred awe."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 309156.0,
      "end_time": 313810.0,
      "text": "So those are the three lessons I took with me from midwifery."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 314253.0,
      "end_time": 316698.0,
      "text": "One: uncover your soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 317376.0,
      "end_time": 323544.0,
      "text": "Two: when things get difficult or painful, try to stay open."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 323568.0,
      "end_time": 327501.0,
      "text": "And three: every now and then, step off your hamster wheel"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 327928.0,
      "end_time": 329550.0,
      "text": "into deep time."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 330946.0,
      "end_time": 334133.0,
      "text": "Those lessons have served me throughout my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 334855.0,
      "end_time": 337314.0,
      "text": "but they really served me recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 337338.0,
      "end_time": 341926.0,
      "text": "when I took on the most important job of my life thus far."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 342572.0,
      "end_time": 346938.0,
      "text": "Two years ago, my younger sister came out of remission"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 346962.0,
      "end_time": 349320.0,
      "text": "from a rare blood cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 349719.0,
      "end_time": 354420.0,
      "text": "and the only treatment left for her was a bone marrow transplant."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 354708.0,
      "end_time": 357797.0,
      "text": "And against the odds, we found a match for her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 357821.0,
      "end_time": 359731.0,
      "text": "who turned out to be me."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 360794.0,
      "end_time": 363573.0,
      "text": "I come from a family of four girls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 364750.0,
      "end_time": 370488.0,
      "text": "and when my sisters found out that I was my sister&#39;s perfect genetic match,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 370512.0,
      "end_time": 372842.0,
      "text": "their reaction was, \"Really? You?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 372866.0,
      "end_time": 374248.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 374273.0,
      "end_time": 376429.0,
      "text": "\"A perfect match for her?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 376453.0,
      "end_time": 378982.0,
      "text": "Which is pretty typical for siblings."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 379488.0,
      "end_time": 382197.0,
      "text": "In a sibling society, there&#39;s lots of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 382221.0,
      "end_time": 386418.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s love and there&#39;s friendship and there&#39;s protection."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 386442.0,
      "end_time": 388980.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s also jealousy"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 388603.0,
      "end_time": 389887.0,
      "text": "and competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 390600.0,
      "end_time": 393330.0,
      "text": "and rejection and attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 393867.0,
      "end_time": 399805.0,
      "text": "In siblinghood, that&#39;s where we start assembling many of those first layers"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 399829.0,
      "end_time": 401316.0,
      "text": "that cover our soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 402106.0,
      "end_time": 405109.0,
      "text": "When I discovered I was my sister&#39;s match,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 405133.0,
      "end_time": 406849.0,
      "text": "I went into research mode."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 407194.0,
      "end_time": 408784.0,
      "text": "And I discovered that"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 410280.0,
      "end_time": 412762.0,
      "text": "the premise of transplants is pretty straightforward."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 412786.0,
      "end_time": 416460.0,
      "text": "You destroy all the bone marrow in the cancer patient"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 416700.0,
      "end_time": 418806.0,
      "text": "with massive doses of chemotherapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 419293.0,
      "end_time": 421703.0,
      "text": "and then you replace that marrow"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 421727.0,
      "end_time": 425566.0,
      "text": "with several million healthy marrow cells from a donor."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 425937.0,
      "end_time": 427743.0,
      "text": "And then you do everything you can"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 427767.0,
      "end_time": 432520.0,
      "text": "to make sure that those new cells engraft in the patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 432760.0,
      "end_time": 436974.0,
      "text": "I also learned that bone marrow transplants are fraught with danger."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 437468.0,
      "end_time": 442308.0,
      "text": "If my sister made it through the near-lethal chemotherapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 442734.0,
      "end_time": 445918.0,
      "text": "she still would face other challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 445942.0,
      "end_time": 448252.0,
      "text": "My cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 448863.0,
      "end_time": 451370.0,
      "text": "might attack her body."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 451843.0,
      "end_time": 454822.0,
      "text": "And her body might reject my cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 454846.0,
      "end_time": 457291.0,
      "text": "They call this rejection or attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 457315.0,
      "end_time": 458941.0,
      "text": "and both could kill her."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 459583.0,
      "end_time": 461575.0,
      "text": "Rejection. Attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 462910.0,
      "end_time": 464282.0,
      "text": "Those words had a familiar ring"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 464306.0,
      "end_time": 466779.0,
      "text": "in the context of being siblings."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 467843.0,
      "end_time": 470652.0,
      "text": "My sister and I had a long history of love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 470676.0,
      "end_time": 473967.0,
      "text": "but we also had a long history of rejection and attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 474487.0,
      "end_time": 478484.0,
      "text": "from minor misunderstandings to bigger betrayals."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 479172.0,
      "end_time": 481306.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t have the kind of the relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 481330.0,
      "end_time": 483455.0,
      "text": "where we talked about the deeper stuff;"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 483887.0,
      "end_time": 488567.0,
      "text": "but, like many siblings and like people in all kinds of relationships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 488987.0,
      "end_time": 491941.0,
      "text": "we were hesitant to tell our truths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 491965.0,
      "end_time": 494842.0,
      "text": "to reveal our wounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 494867.0,
      "end_time": 496718.0,
      "text": "to admit our wrongdoings."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 497180.0,
      "end_time": 502710.0,
      "text": "But when I learned about the dangers of rejection or attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 502950.0,
      "end_time": 504399.0,
      "text": "I thought, it&#39;s time to change this."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 505730.0,
      "end_time": 509888.0,
      "text": "What if we left the bone marrow transplant up to the doctors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 509913.0,
      "end_time": 515722.0,
      "text": "but did something that we later came to call our \"soul marrow transplant?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 516205.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520191.00000000006,
      "text": "What if we faced any pain we had caused each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 520215.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522922.00000000006,
      "text": "and instead of rejection or attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 523453.0,
      "end_time": 524770.0,
      "text": "could we listen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 525272.0,
      "end_time": 526698.0,
      "text": "Could we forgive?"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 527116.0,
      "end_time": 528556.0,
      "text": "Could we merge?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 528580.0,
      "end_time": 532510.0,
      "text": "Would that teach our cells to do the same?"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 533431.0,
      "end_time": 538244.0,
      "text": "To woo my skeptical sister, I turned to my parents&#39; holy text:"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 538268.0,
      "end_time": 539869.0,
      "text": "the New Yorker Magazine."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 539893.0,
      "end_time": 541809.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 541833.0,
      "end_time": 545404.0,
      "text": "I sent her a cartoon from its pages"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 545428.0,
      "end_time": 549530.0,
      "text": "as a way of explaining why we should visit a therapist"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 549770.0,
      "end_time": 554443.0,
      "text": "before having my bone marrow harvested and transplanted into her body."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 554467.0,
      "end_time": 555712.0,
      "text": "Here it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 555736.0,
      "end_time": 559850.0,
      "text": "\"I have never forgiven him for that thing I made up in my head.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 559874.0,
      "end_time": 562281.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 562305.0,
      "end_time": 564251.0,
      "text": "I told my sister"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 564950.0,
      "end_time": 567787.0,
      "text": "we had probably been doing the same thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 567811.0,
      "end_time": 573531.0,
      "text": "carting around made-up stories in our heads that kept us separate."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 574184.0,
      "end_time": 577760.0,
      "text": "And I told her that after the transplant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 577100.0,
      "end_time": 579694.0,
      "text": "all of the blood flowing in her veins"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 579718.0,
      "end_time": 581199.0,
      "text": "would be my blood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 581223.0,
      "end_time": 583642.0,
      "text": "made from my marrow cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 584301.0,
      "end_time": 588530.0,
      "text": "and that inside the nucleus of each of those cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 588554.0,
      "end_time": 590819.0,
      "text": "is a complete set of my DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 591351.0,
      "end_time": 594731.0,
      "text": "\"I will be swimming around in you for the rest of your life,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 594755.0,
      "end_time": 597514.0,
      "text": "I told my slightly horrified sister."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 597538.0,
      "end_time": 599718.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 599742.0,
      "end_time": 602829.0,
      "text": "\"I think we better clean up our relationship.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 604168.0,
      "end_time": 607488.0,
      "text": "A health crisis makes people do all sorts of risky things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 607512.0,
      "end_time": 611530.0,
      "text": "like quitting a job or jumping out of an airplane"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 611603.0,
      "end_time": 613593.0,
      "text": "and, in the case of my sister,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 613618.0,
      "end_time": 617352.0,
      "text": "saying \"yes\" to several therapy sessions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 617723.0,
      "end_time": 621414.0,
      "text": "during which we got down to the marrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 623588.0,
      "end_time": 627981.0,
      "text": "We looked at and released years of stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 628500.0,
      "end_time": 630860.0,
      "text": "and assumptions about each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 630110.0,
      "end_time": 632188.0,
      "text": "and blame and shame"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 632212.0,
      "end_time": 635750.0,
      "text": "until all that was left was love."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 638175.0,
      "end_time": 642363.0,
      "text": "People have said I was brave to undergo the bone marrow harvest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 642387.0,
      "end_time": 643656.0,
      "text": "but I don&#39;t think so."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 644100.0,
      "end_time": 646190.0,
      "text": "What felt brave to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 646214.0,
      "end_time": 649399.0,
      "text": "was that other kind of harvest and transplant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 649423.0,
      "end_time": 651319.0,
      "text": "the soul marrow transplant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 651772.0,
      "end_time": 655750.0,
      "text": "getting emotionally naked with another human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 655774.0,
      "end_time": 659243.0,
      "text": "putting aside pride and defensiveness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 659267.0,
      "end_time": 660903.0,
      "text": "lifting the layers"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 661559.0,
      "end_time": 665650.0,
      "text": "and sharing with each other our vulnerable souls."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 666416.0,
      "end_time": 669215.0,
      "text": "I called on those midwife lessons:"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 669239.0,
      "end_time": 670865.0,
      "text": "uncover your soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 671963.0,
      "end_time": 674603.0,
      "text": "Open to what&#39;s scary and painful."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 674628.0,
      "end_time": 676484.0,
      "text": "Look for the sacred awe."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 677872.0,
      "end_time": 681137.0,
      "text": "Here I am with my marrow cells after the harvest."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 681161.0,
      "end_time": 683600.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s they call it -- \"harvest,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 683850.0,
      "end_time": 686285.0,
      "text": "like it&#39;s some kind of bucolic farm-to-table event --"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 686309.0,
      "end_time": 687467.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 687491.0,
      "end_time": 689983.0,
      "text": "Which I can assure you it is not."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 691522.0,
      "end_time": 694857.0,
      "text": "And here is my brave, brave sister"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 694881.0,
      "end_time": 696577.0,
      "text": "receiving my cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 697768.0,
      "end_time": 701706.0,
      "text": "After the transplant, we began to spend more and more time together."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 702289.0,
      "end_time": 704568.0,
      "text": "It was as if we were little girls again."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 705537.0,
      "end_time": 708505.0,
      "text": "The past and the present merged."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 708529.0,
      "end_time": 710735.0,
      "text": "We entered deep time."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 711331.0,
      "end_time": 715607.0,
      "text": "I left the hamster wheel of work and life"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 715631.0,
      "end_time": 717293.0,
      "text": "to join my sister"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 717992.0,
      "end_time": 719988.0,
      "text": "on that lonely island"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 720444.0,
      "end_time": 722219.0,
      "text": "of illness and healing."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 722948.0,
      "end_time": 724790.0,
      "text": "We spent months together --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 724815.0,
      "end_time": 726577.0,
      "text": "in the isolation unit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 726601.0,
      "end_time": 728959.0,
      "text": "in the hospital and in her home."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 730411.0,
      "end_time": 732990.0,
      "text": "Our fast-paced society"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 732124.0,
      "end_time": 737284.0,
      "text": "does not support or even value this kind of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 737308.0,
      "end_time": 740941.0,
      "text": "We see it as a disruption of real life and important work."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 741426.0,
      "end_time": 745654.0,
      "text": "We worry about the emotional drain and the financial cost --"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 745678.0,
      "end_time": 749253.0,
      "text": "and, yes, there is a financial cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 749277.0,
      "end_time": 750951.0,
      "text": "But I was paid"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 751590.0,
      "end_time": 756457.0,
      "text": "in the kind of currency our culture seems to have forgotten all about."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 757132.0,
      "end_time": 759271.0,
      "text": "I was paid in love."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 759629.0,
      "end_time": 761374.0,
      "text": "I was paid in soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 761398.0,
      "end_time": 763568.0,
      "text": "I was paid in my sister."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 764792.0,
      "end_time": 769984.0,
      "text": "My sister said the year after transplant was the best year of her life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 770800.0,
      "end_time": 771257.0,
      "text": "which was surprising."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 771281.0,
      "end_time": 773728.0,
      "text": "She suffered so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 774364.0,
      "end_time": 777596.0,
      "text": "But she said life never tasted as sweet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 778400.0,
      "end_time": 780748.0,
      "text": "and that because of the soul-baring"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 780772.0,
      "end_time": 783318.0,
      "text": "and the truth-telling we had done with each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 783721.0,
      "end_time": 787537.0,
      "text": "she became more unapologetically herself"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 787561.0,
      "end_time": 788952.0,
      "text": "with everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 788976.0,
      "end_time": 791944.0,
      "text": "She said things she&#39;d always needed to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 791968.0,
      "end_time": 794756.0,
      "text": "She did things she always wanted to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 795263.0,
      "end_time": 797222.0,
      "text": "The same happened for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 797246.0,
      "end_time": 802595.0,
      "text": "I became braver about being authentic with the people in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 803917.0,
      "end_time": 805610.0,
      "text": "I said my truths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 805634.0,
      "end_time": 810229.0,
      "text": "but more important than that, I sought the truth of others."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 811713.0,
      "end_time": 815970.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t until the final chapter of this story"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 815121.0,
      "end_time": 818569.0,
      "text": "that I realized just how well midwifery had trained me."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 819214.0,
      "end_time": 822129.0,
      "text": "After that best year of my sister&#39;s life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 822153.0,
      "end_time": 824154.0,
      "text": "the cancer came roaring back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 824702.0,
      "end_time": 827974.0,
      "text": "and this time there was nothing more the doctors could do."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 827998.0,
      "end_time": 830664.0,
      "text": "They gave her just a couple of months to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 832196.0,
      "end_time": 834573.0,
      "text": "The night before my sister died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 835163.0,
      "end_time": 837871.0,
      "text": "I sat by her bedside."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 837895.0,
      "end_time": 840178.0,
      "text": "She was so small and thin."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 840766.0,
      "end_time": 843289.0,
      "text": "I could see the blood pulsing in her neck."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 843869.0,
      "end_time": 847414.0,
      "text": "It was my blood, her blood, our blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 848462.0,
      "end_time": 851314.0,
      "text": "When she died, part of me would die, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 852687.0,
      "end_time": 857359.0,
      "text": "I tried to make sense of it all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 857383.0,
      "end_time": 859513.0,
      "text": "how becoming one with each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 860800.0,
      "end_time": 862170.0,
      "text": "had made us more ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 862410.0,
      "end_time": 863548.0,
      "text": "our soul selves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 864249.0,
      "end_time": 869442.0,
      "text": "and how by facing and opening to the pain of our past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 869466.0,
      "end_time": 871965.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d finally been delivered to each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 872651.0,
      "end_time": 874901.0,
      "text": "and how by stepping out of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 874925.0,
      "end_time": 877333.0,
      "text": "we would now be connected forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 878980.0,
      "end_time": 881910.0,
      "text": "My sister left me with so many things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 882365.0,
      "end_time": 885850.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to leave you now with just one of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 885565.0,
      "end_time": 889795.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have to wait for a life-or-death situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 890497.0,
      "end_time": 893616.0,
      "text": "to clean up the relationships that matter to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 893640.0,
      "end_time": 896263.0,
      "text": "to offer the marrow of your soul"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 897157.0,
      "end_time": 899345.0,
      "text": "and to seek it in another."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 900297.0,
      "end_time": 902215.0,
      "text": "We can all do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 902239.0,
      "end_time": 907820.0,
      "text": "We can be like a new kind of first responder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 907106.0,
      "end_time": 911309.0,
      "text": "like the one to take the first courageous step"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 911906.0,
      "end_time": 913657.0,
      "text": "toward the other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 913682.0,
      "end_time": 916927.0,
      "text": "and to do something or try to do something"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 916951.0,
      "end_time": 920730.0,
      "text": "other than rejection or attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 920545.0,
      "end_time": 922711.0,
      "text": "We can do this with our siblings"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 922735.0,
      "end_time": 924137.0,
      "text": "and our mates"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 924161.0,
      "end_time": 926416.0,
      "text": "and our friends and our colleagues."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 926441.0,
      "end_time": 929690.0,
      "text": "We can do this with the disconnection"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 929930.0,
      "end_time": 931843.0,
      "text": "and the discord all around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 932410.0,
      "end_time": 936760.0,
      "text": "We can do this for the soul of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 936629.0,
      "end_time": 937820.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 937844.0,
      "end_time": 943840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}